.gstack/
/.gadgetron/

# Local operator config — copy gadgetron.example.toml and customize.
/gadgetron.toml

# Tool-specific session state and native subagent adapters.
# Per AGENTS.md the project is tool-independent — adapters stay user-level
# (e.g. ~/.claude/agents/) and do not ship in the repo.
/.claude/

# graphify: cache directory + volatile scratch files regenerated on every
# commit / pull via the post-* hooks. The curated surfaces
# (`GRAPH_REPORT.md`, `graph.json`, `graph.html`) stay committed; the
# cache / scratch files do not — they produce diff churn on every commit
# without adding reviewable signal.
graphify-out/cache/
graphify-out/.graphify_*
